"title": "4324: dross",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4324: dross",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Impurities removed from molten metal during refining. In a spiritual sense, wicked people whom God removes in judgment, and also impurities in believers which are removed by discipline and trials.</p>\n<h2>God removes the wicked like dross</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:119\">PSA 119:119</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:28\">ISA 30:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:28-Jer6:30\">JER 6:28–6:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:19-Ezek22:22\">EZK 22:19–22:22</a></p>\n<h2>Dross as a metaphor for impurity in God's people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:18\">EZK 22:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:21-Isa1:23\">ISA 1:21–1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:11-Ezek24:13\">EZK 24:11–24:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:25\">EZK 36:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:8-Amos9:10\">AMO 9:8–9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:21\">JAS 1:21</a></p>\n<h2>God purges the dross from his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:25-Isa1:26\">ISA 1:25–1:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:3\">PRO 17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:4\">PRO 25:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:10\">DAN 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:2-Mal3:3\">MAL 3:2–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>By the blood of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:1\">ZEC 13:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:14\">HEB 9:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:7\">1JN 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>By the work of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:25-Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:25–36:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:11-Matt3:12\">MAT 3:11–3:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:16-Luke3:17\">LUK 3:16–3:17</a></p>\n<h3>By testing and affliction</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:10-Ps66:12\">PSA 66:10–66:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:10\">ISA 48:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:7\">JER 9:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:9\">ZEC 13:9</a></p>",
